    <!-- Content 1  -->

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-around mt-32 h-full mb-48">
        <img src="./assets/art1.jpg" alt="..." class="shadow-2xl rounded w-aut h-auto align-middle border-none" />
        <div class=" flex flex-col max-w-xl -tracking-tight justify-center text-center items-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 "><span
                    class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r to-emerald-600 from-sky-400">Welcome to Club
                    Artisti !</span><br> Only Art Club of SMIT</h1>
            <div class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-500 m-4">Our club is a vibrant hub of creativity where members
                come
                together to share their passion for art, learn new techniques, and showcase their work. Our website is
                your gateway to all the exciting things happening in our club.
            </div>

            <div class="w-3/12 flex justify-end mobile:hidden mt-4">
                <a class=" inline-block py-2 px-6 bg-black hover:bg-slate-700 text-sm text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition duration-200"
                    href="" target="_blank">Explore More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Content 2  -->

    <div class="bg-orange-100 mt-12 flex flex-col justify-start items-center" id="aboutus">
        <h1 class="mt-12 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 "><span
                class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r to-pink-400 from-yellow-400 from-red-400">Our
                Journey as a Club</span><br> </h1>
        <div class="px-48 text-lg font-normal text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">We are the only art club in our college,
            and our journey has been a colorful and creative one. We started as a small group of passionate artists who
            wanted to share our love of art with our fellow students. Over time, our membership has grown, and we have
            become a vibrant community of artists and art enthusiasts.<br>
            One of the highlights of our journey has been our involvement in the college's art events. We have organized
            exhibitions, art contests, and workshops that have showcased the talents of our members and inspired others
            to pursue their artistic passions. We have also collaborated with other clubs and organizations to bring the
            arts to the wider college community.
        </div>
        
    </div>

    <!-- footer -->
    <!-- Thank you for choosing to be a part of our Art Club. We look forward to creating and sharing art with you! -->
